	(<f> ^text |Think about it, ponies are vastly superior to humans. For example, think about how pathetic it is to walk upright. The pony's body is much stronger and more optimized. Human behavior is unstable and destructive. And the pony's emotional system provides greater stability to the individual by prioritizing the generation of fun and magic of friendship. Do you agree?|)
}

